import { Box, List, ListItem, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon } from '@mui/material'

import React from 'react'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <Box bgcolor="skyblue" flex={1} p={2} sx={{display:{xs: "none", sm: "block" }}}>
            <List>
                <ListItem disablePadding>
                    <ListItemButton>
                        <ListItemIcon>
                            <InboxIcon />
                        </ListItemIcon>
                    </ListItemButton>
                </ListItem>
            </List>
            </Box>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
